General Information

Remifemin Menopause Symptom Relief is a remarkable plant extract used by millions of satisfied women across the World. A natural product for women with over 40 years of medical research and international studies.

Remifemin has proven to be extremely effective in relieving symptoms experienced during pre-menopause, menopause and post menopause.

Hot Flushes, Anxiety, Mood Swings, Night Sweats, and other menopausal symptoms.

Remifemin is recognised as one of Germany's foremost natural products and is used in over 20 countries around the World.

Directions

Take 1 tablet two times daily, one in the morning, one in the evening, if desired clinical studies have shown that up to 4 tablets are tolerable.
